message.body: Hey Jes, :) I've been dreaming alot lately which is making me think of you. Are you up for a phone date? I'm here now and could wait till after 9 if you want.
Cant tonite. Want to try for tomorrow?
In class till 9:30. I will get the train at 9:32 or 9:46. I could call then but is that too late? Thursday would work too.
Maybe we could do Thursday? Not sure i will be up for a long convo that late.
Sounds good. Lets call each other Thursday at 9.
